articles.description: The next installment in the Bridgerton universe follows Queen Charlotte and King George, decades before Daphne and the Duke. Check out the first teaser. Queen Charlotte: A Bridgerton Story hits Netflix on May 4.
articles.content: One Queen to rule them all
